  "recipe_notes": [
    "Use boneless chicken breast. Make sure that this is already flat. If not, cover the chicken with a plastic wrap such as cling wrap or the likes and gently pound with the flat side of the meat tenderizer tool.",
    "Cook the chicken breast by boiling for 15 minutes. Let it cool down. Remove the skin (if any) and shred the meat into pieces."
